      public void zwyciezca()
      This method is called when it is the end of the game. It shows the player how many mistakes he made and displays end of game window objects.

    • rozpocznijGre

      public void rozpocznijGre​(int x)
      This method starts the game. It has parameter x which is the number of the level chosen by the player. When "Zacznij Gre" button is clicked this function is called.

    • actionPerformed

      public void actionPerformed​(ActionEvent click)
      This method is for registering events such as mouse clicks so that the programme knows where the user clicked. There are multiple if conditions inside of this method. If certain condition is satisfied (when player clicks on a certain button) other methods are called as well.
      Specified by:
      actionPerformed in interface ActionListener
